    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 28
      },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Ecommerce alert catalog (`ecommerce-app-rules`)\n\n| Alert | Severity | Symptom |\n|-------|----------|---------|\n| `EcommerceServiceDown` | critical | Scrape target down 2m |\n| `EcommerceHighErrorRate` | warning | 5xx > 5% for 5m |\n| `EcommerceHighLatency` | warning | p95 > 1s for 10m |\n| `EcommercePodCrashLooping` | warning | >3 restarts in 15m |\n| `EcommerceHighPaymentFailureRate` | warning | Payment failures > 10% |\n| `EcommerceRabbitMQDown` / `EcommerceRedisDown` | critical | Dependency not ready |\n"
      }
    }
  ]
